show.description:
She’s bold, impulsive, and wants it all—no matter the cost. But when her stubborn choices spiral into misunderstandings and chaos, life turns into an emotional roller coaster.
A fun-filled tale of ambition, confusion, and heart—where every mistake brings drama and a lesson.
